text: Henry Crawley (19 August 1865 - 18 June 1931) was an English cricketer. He played four first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club between 1885 and 1887. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1865 births Category:1931 deaths Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:People from Highgate Category:Marylebone Cricket Club cricketers Category:C.
